data.description: Beautiful home in nice quiet neighborhood!! Don't miss out on this completely updated house in the highly sought after White Oak ISD area.  With 2 bedrooms and full bath upstairs and 2 bedrooms and full bath down stairs this home has plenty of space to accommodate everyone!  The huge backyard is perfect for entertaining with its covered patio and open deck extension all completely enclosed with a privacy fence there is plenty of room to add a pool, playground or anything else you desire!  There is also a large 20x30 functional workshop with electric, a roll up door, and private gate entrance! This home has brand new paint through out the inside and outside, all new flooring through out, new light fixtures and knobs, new appliances, new toilets, and beautiful new granite countertops in the kitchen!  This one won't last long!!! Call to schedule your private tour today!
